config EDMAC
        tristate "Lotus EDMAC Controller support"
        depends on ARCH_XMFALCON  || ARCH_XMORCA
        select DMA_ENGINE
        select DMA_VIRTUAL_CHANNELS
        help
          The Direction Memory Access(EDMA) is a high-speed data transfer
          operation. It supports data read/write between peripherals and
          memories without using the CPU.
          Lotus EDMA Controller(EDMAC) directly transfers data between
          a memory and a peripheral, or between memories.
          This avoids the CPU intervention and reduces the interrupt handling
          overhead of the CPU.
